{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"It's amazing, when you meet a head of state and you say,"},{"time":2000,"text":"\"What is your most precious natural resource?\" --"},{"time":6000,"text":"they will not say children at first."},{"time":8000,"text":"And then when you say children,"},{"time":10000,"text":"they will pretty quickly agree with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":19000,"text":"(Video): We're traveling today with"},{"time":21000,"text":"the Minister of Defense of Colombia,"},{"time":24000,"text":"head of the army and the head of the police,"},{"time":26000,"text":"and we're dropping off 650 laptops"},{"time":29000,"text":"today to children"},{"time":31000,"text":"who have no television, no telephone"},{"time":33000,"text":"and have been in a community"},{"time":35000,"text":"cut off from the rest of the world"},{"time":37000,"text":"for the past 40 years. \n"}]},{"cues":[{"time":40000,"text":"The importance of delivering laptops to this region"},{"time":43000,"text":"is connecting kids who have otherwise been unconnected"},{"time":46000,"text":"because of the FARC,"},{"time":48000,"text":"the guerrillas that started off 40 years ago"},{"time":51000,"text":"as a political movement and then became a drug movement."},{"time":56000,"text":"There are one billion children in the world,"},{"time":58000,"text":"and 50 percent of them don't have electricity"},{"time":60000,"text":"at home or at school."},{"time":63000,"text":"And in some countries -- let me pick Afghanistan --"},{"time":65000,"text":"75 percent of the little girls don't go to school."},{"time":68000,"text":"And I don't mean that they drop out of school"},{"time":70000,"text":"in the third or fourth grade -- they don't go."}]},{"cues":[{"time":72000,"text":"So in the three years"},{"time":74000,"text":"since I talked at TED and showed a prototype,"},{"time":77000,"text":"it's gone from an idea"},{"time":79000,"text":"to a real laptop."},{"time":82000,"text":"We have half a million laptops today"},{"time":84000,"text":"in the hands of children."},{"time":87000,"text":"We have about a quarter of a million in transit"},{"time":89000,"text":"to those and other children,"},{"time":92000,"text":"and then there are another quarter of a million more"},{"time":96000,"text":"that are being ordered at this moment."},{"time":98000,"text":"So, in rough numbers, there are a million laptops."},{"time":100000,"text":"That's smaller than I predicted --"},{"time":102000,"text":"I predicted three to 10 million --"},{"time":104000,"text":"but is still a very large number."}]},{"cues":[{"time":106000,"text":"In Colombia, we have about 3,000 laptops."},{"time":110000,"text":"It's the Minister of Defense with whom we're working,"},{"time":113000,"text":"not the Minister of Education, because it is seen as"},{"time":116000,"text":"a strategic defense issue"},{"time":118000,"text":"in the sense of liberating these zones"},{"time":123000,"text":"that had been completely closed off,"},{"time":125000,"text":"in which the people who had been causing, if you will,"},{"time":129000,"text":"40 years' worth of bombings and kidnappings"},{"time":133000,"text":"and assassinations lived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135000,"text":"And suddenly,"},{"time":137000,"text":"the kids have connected laptops."},{"time":139000,"text":"They've leapfrogged."},{"time":141000,"text":"The change is absolutely monumental,"},{"time":145000,"text":"because it's not just opening it up,"},{"time":147000,"text":"but it's opening it up to the rest of the world."},{"time":150000,"text":"So yes, they're building roads, yes, they're putting in telephone,"},{"time":152000,"text":"yes, there will be television."},{"time":154000,"text":"But the kids six to 12 years old"},{"time":156000,"text":"are surfing the Internet in Spanish and in local languages,"},{"time":160000,"text":"so the children grow up"},{"time":162000,"text":"with access to information,"},{"time":164000,"text":"with a window into the rest of the world."},{"time":167000,"text":"Before, they were closed off."}]},{"cues":[{"time":169000,"text":"Interestingly enough, in other countries,"},{"time":171000,"text":"it will be the Minister of Finance who sees it"},{"time":173000,"text":"as an engine of economic growth."},{"time":177000,"text":"And that engine is going to see the results in 20 years."},{"time":181000,"text":"It's not going to happen, you know, in one year,"},{"time":184000,"text":"but it's an important, deeply economic"},{"time":187000,"text":"and cultural change"},{"time":189000,"text":"that happens through children."},{"time":192000,"text":"Thirty-one countries in total are involved,"},{"time":194000,"text":"and in the case of Uruguay,"},{"time":197000,"text":"half the children already have them,"},{"time":199000,"text":"and by the middle of 2009,"},{"time":202000,"text":"every single child in Uruguay will have a laptop --"},{"time":205000,"text":"a little green laptop."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207000,"text":"Now what are some of the results?"},{"time":209000,"text":"Some of the results"},{"time":211000,"text":"that go across every single country"},{"time":214000,"text":"include teachers saying"},{"time":216000,"text":"they have never loved teaching so much,"},{"time":219000,"text":"and reading comprehension"},{"time":221000,"text":"measured by third parties -- not by us -- skyrockets."},{"time":225000,"text":"Probably the most important thing we see"},{"time":228000,"text":"is children teaching parents."},{"time":231000,"text":"They own the laptops. They take them home."},{"time":234000,"text":"And so when I met with three children from the schools,"},{"time":237000,"text":"who had traveled all day to come to Bogota,"},{"time":241000,"text":"one of the three children brought her mother."},{"time":244000,"text":"And the reason she brought her mother"},{"time":246000,"text":"is that this six-year-old child"},{"time":249000,"text":"had been teaching her mother"},{"time":251000,"text":"how to read and write."},{"time":253000,"text":"Her mother had not gone to primary school."},{"time":256000,"text":"And this is such an inversion,"},{"time":258000,"text":"and such a wonderful example"},{"time":261000,"text":"of children being the agents of change."}]},{"cues":[{"time":265000,"text":"So now, in closing, people say,"},{"time":267000,"text":"now why laptops?"},{"time":269000,"text":"Laptops are a luxury; it's like giving them iPods. No."},{"time":272000,"text":"The reason you want laptops"},{"time":274000,"text":"is that the word is education, not laptop."},{"time":278000,"text":"This is an education project, not a laptop project."},{"time":281000,"text":"They need to learn learning. And then, just think --"},{"time":283000,"text":"they can have, let's say, 100 books."},{"time":285000,"text":"In a village, you have 100 laptops,"},{"time":288000,"text":"each with a different set of 100 books,"},{"time":291000,"text":"and so that village suddenly has 10,000 books."},{"time":294000,"text":"You and I didn't have 10,000 books when we went to primary school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298000,"text":"Sometimes school is under a tree,"},{"time":300000,"text":"or in many cases, the teacher has only a fifth-grade education,"},{"time":304000,"text":"so you need a collaborative model of learning,"},{"time":307000,"text":"not just building more schools and training more teachers,"},{"time":309000,"text":"which you have to do anyway."},{"time":311000,"text":"So we're once again doing \"Give One, Get One.\""},{"time":314000,"text":"Last year, we ran a \"Give One, Get One\" program,"},{"time":316000,"text":"and it generated over 100,000 laptops"},{"time":320000,"text":"that we were then able to give free."},{"time":323000,"text":"And by being a zero-dollar laptop,"},{"time":325000,"text":"we can go to countries that can't afford it at all."},{"time":328000,"text":"And that's what we did. We went to Haiti,"},{"time":331000,"text":"we went to Rwanda, Afghanistan,"},{"time":333000,"text":"Ethiopia, Mongolia."},{"time":336000,"text":"Places that are not markets,"},{"time":338000,"text":"seeding it with the principles of"},{"time":341000,"text":"saturation, connectivity, low ages, etc."},{"time":344000,"text":"And then we can actually roll out large numbers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":348000,"text":"So think of it this way:"},{"time":350000,"text":"think of it as inoculating children"},{"time":353000,"text":"against ignorance."},{"time":356000,"text":"And think of the laptop as a vaccine."},{"time":358000,"text":"You don't vaccinate a few children."},{"time":360000,"text":"You vaccinate all the children in an area."}]}]}